# Rule 300: Discovery Master

> Complete discovery rule set for AI-powered product discovery

## Core Principle

**No engineering work begins until the Opportunity Score is ≥ 8.0/10. All discovery outputs must be complete and validated before proceeding to validation planning or engineering.**

